		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/18/mortgage-reform-is-worth-the-small-extra-cost-to-borrowers/" data-title="Mortgage Reform Is Worth the Small Extra Cost to Borrowers" data-description="The higher cost for borrowers in a Senate bill reforming Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac corresponds to the protection for taxpayers that was missing in the old system, writes an economist. ">
